This Privacy Policy describes how your information is handled when you use our IPTV Player application.

1. Information Collection and Use
Our application is designed as a tool to play IPTV content. We do not collect, store, or share any personal information, usage data, or any other type of sensitive information from our users. The application operates without requiring any user registration or data input.

2. Media Content
The application does not provide any media or content. Users are responsible for providing their own content (such as IPTV playlists). We do not have access to, nor do we monitor or store the content you stream through the application.

3. Permissions
The application may request certain permissions (such as internet access) strictly to perform its core function of streaming the content you provide. No data accessed through these permissions is transmitted to us or any third party.

4. Third-Party Services
The application is hosted on GitHub and may be distributed through the Huawei AppGallery. These third-party platforms may collect information according to their own privacy policies. We recommend reviewing their respective policies for more information.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through our GitHub repository.
